description "Imperial Mortar Trooper [Elite Trooper]

^5Pros^7: Heavy Hitter armed with a Rocket Launcher capable of taking down groups of enemies.
^1Cons^7: Slower Movement compared to other classes due to weapon weight.

^2Weapons:
- Heavy Melee
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- PLX-1 Rocket Launcher (3 Rockets)
- 3 Frag Grenades
- 2 Trip Mines
- 1 Thermal Detonator

^8Attributes:
- Blast Armour
- Stamina (3)
- 1 Reinforcement

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]

Armed with Heavy Explosives, the Imperial Artillery Trooper, otherwise known as 'Mortar Stormtrooper' can be easily identified by their Yellow Markings."